{"tid":577282,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"今日買轉插唔小心買到山寨貨，但係蘋果包裝，可以點做","createTime":"2018-03-01T15:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T06:40:05.000Z","uid":37796,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"464daf217ffc44fa1c84d6647e3b82bfad2fc55b","tid":577282,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"本身諗住想買隻type-c =&gt; HDMI 轉插for macbook pro用<br />\n打算都係買副廠 因為之前用過隻副廠都ok（不過個隻係插兩個type c 頭）<br />\n<br />\n係黃金間細鋪見到，問佢咩價，個店員就答138<br />\n我見到係一開三頭，見過同事用，佢個陣買二百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心諗 咁平 咪買左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然包裝睇正面又唔知咩廠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/231714_e27461e01b893e9ed11391aacffc72b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F231714_e27461e01b893e9ed11391aacffc72b4.jpg&h=9d19309e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係開出黎連膠袋呀，套都冇<br />\n見到後面寫住係蘋果公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/231903_b473ccbdd3372aa5c498f025b3889f89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F231903_b473ccbdd3372aa5c498f025b3889f89.jpg&h=19f7d992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個陣先發現自己中左伏，睇返個樣同包裝個樣都唔同<br />\n<br />\n用落個hdmi 頭又唔得 （先會打咁大篇野）<br />\n可以點做？報唔報得海關"},{"pid":"4cbbca7075fc3f9c71a6426a6b61cf4cfd174ccd","tid":577282,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"買個陣我又冇開包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5228f78239e6c40ec5901d95f2830596b10c914","tid":577282,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124f