like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84932ad4eacc34c4ccc7e57c395c5b628d9cfbbb","tid":577282,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2f712068c1b1b5e610038539a7580862ef187e","tid":577282,"uid":11388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"下面印果兩行字周街都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"成舊水既教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:47:41.000Z","msg":"根本出深水埗就係買水貨，行貨點會揀深水埗買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫水貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 水貨係指通過合法或唔合法嘅渠道，繞過當地貨物嘅總代理而入口嘅貨物，通常水貨係冇原廠保養嘅。有代理同保養嘅叫「行貨」。<br />\n<br />\n水貨有別於冒牌貨、A貨、B貨（假貨），或者老鼠貨（偷返嚟賣嘅正貨），水貨係原裝正貨。水貨嘅售價通常平過行貨，但係有啲情況下水貨會貴過行貨，例如當行貨有排都未輪到某地區賣而當地又好多人想要，噉樣水貨就會貴過行貨嘞，基本上係睇地區需求嚟定價錢。</span>"},{"pid":"7589f49aa757bce4c4a158ba828a0dfb3c3b6e56","tid":577282,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:08:40.000Z","msg":"apple d 野邊會有特價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465fe093d8b551af208bb98b9aedd48826836223","tid":577282,"uid":10637,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"13b2127d77fd72eb9e1225683a22a512f8d92e93","tid":577282,"uid":49136,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8d7172af1cece3e3e8e4b058203c75d0173e29ba","tid":577282,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84932ad4eacc34c4ccc7e57c395c5b628d9cfbbb","tid":577282,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"